# VerifyPDF API key.
#
# 1. Copy this file to ".verifypdf-key" (drop the ".example").
# 2. Replace the line below with your key from the Developers section of
#    https://secure.verifypdf.com  (live keys start key_live_, test keys key_test_).
# 3. Save. The helper scripts read the first non-comment line as the key.
#
# Prefer the VERIFYPDF_API_KEY environment variable for production and CI so the
# secret never lands on disk. This file exists for convenient local use and is
# git-ignored. Never commit a real key or paste it into a chat prompt.

key_live_REPLACE_WITH_YOUR_KEY
